    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，触发条件是DECODE事件，但需要满足guard条件：filePath不为空而且文件要存在。解析完成后，如果AST生成成功，就自动进入extracting状态去提取exports和imports。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "parsing",
        "extracting",
        "AUTO",
        "AST"
