    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我已经把parsing到extracting的自动转换加上了，guard条件是ast is not None。接下来提取完成后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "parsing",
        "extracting",
        "AUTO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "提取到exports和imports之后，如果两者都不为空，就自动进入tracing状态，开始追踪函数内部的调用关系。tracing完成后再自动进入computing状态进行依赖计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "extracting",
        "tracing",
        "computing",
